title: John Digweed Transitions Complete 2012
description:
--------------------------------------
John Digweed - Transitions radio show.
--------------------------------------
(From Proton Radio:)
The most important radio show in house
music needs no introduction, but here 
it goes anyway. John Digweed's 
long-standing weekly 2 hour program 
is legendary, airing for many years 
exclusively on Kiss 100 in London but
now syndicated around the world and 
internet.
--------------------------------------

This torrent contains all the radio 
shows from 2012
